@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sqdfhd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.22
    v0 = v0
    v1 = ((0.28 - wp.exp(v2 + 0.87)) / v0)
    tmp = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.17 - v0 + 0.12)) + 0.59)
    v2 = 0.85
    v1 = (0.26 * (v1 * v1))
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.63) * 0.82) + ((v2 + 0.80 * v0 + 0.55) + tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
